Charles Edwards (English actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Edwards_(English_actor) 0 Charles Edwards (born 1 October 1969) is an English actor, the youngest of four brothers in his family. He graduated from the Guildhall School of Music and Drama in 1992. Charles_Edwards ( born 1_October_1969 ) is an_English_actor , the_youngest of four_brothers in his_family . He graduated from the_Guildhall_School of Music_and_Drama in 1992 .
